room_title: Escape room "White House Down" by Key Quest in Tulsa
room_description: The President is in danger. The door to the safe room is locked and time is running out. Attackers managed to initiate a 60-minute countdown to a nuclear missile launch. Only the President has the counter-code to shut it down. Your mission is to enter the safe room, decipher the clues, find the codes and deliver them to the President. Only you can save the world!
